{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I have an existing "Brand Ambassador Application" form. Please replace its fields and settings with the specification below, keep the Synapex black/white minimal style, and route all submissions to sporting@synapex.store with the subject prefix [Ambassador Application]. Also create a customer record for each submitter and tag it Ambassador Applicant.
    
    Form goals: Collect necessary contact info, sport background, focal sport(s), and content style. Validate clearly, keep the form fast to complete (no unnecessary fields). Email submission details to sporting@synapex.store and show a branded confirmation. Save key answers to customer metafields for future filtering.
    
    Fields: Full Name (text, required, placeholder "First & Last Name"), Email Address (email, required, validate format, placeholder "name@example.com"), Phone Number (tel, optional, placeholder "+1 (_ ) _-"), Location (text, optional, placeholder "City, Country"), Primary Sport (select, required, options: Running, Track & Field, Triathlon, Cycling, CrossFit, Functional Fitness, Soccer, Basketball, Volleyball, Combat Sports, Swimming, Other), Competition Level (select, required, options: Recreational, Amateur, Collegiate, Elite, Professional), Years Active (number, optional, min 0, max 40, placeholder "e.g., 6"), Content Style (checkboxes, required – at least one, options: Training Sessions, Competition Highlights, Recovery & Rehab, Education/Tips, Lifestyle), Primary Platforms (checkboxes, optional, options: Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, Strava, Other), Handles / Links (multi-line text, required, placeholder "Instagram: @handle\nTikTok: @handle\nYouTube: https://…\nStrava: https://…\nOther: https://…"), Typical Posting Frequency (select, optional, options: 1–2x/week, 3–4x/week, 5+x/week), Example Content Links (multi-line text, optional, placeholder "Paste up to 3 URLs to posts or videos you're proud of"), Have you used kinesiology tape before? (radio, required, options: Yes, No), If yes, which brands have you used? (text, conditional: show only if answer = Yes, optional), Tell us briefly about your athletic background (paragraph, required, placeholder "Key achievements, events, or teams…"), Why do you want to represent Synapex? (paragraph, required, placeholder "What makes you a great fit for an athlete-built performance brand?"), Consent & Contact (checkbox, required, label "I confirm my information is accurate and agree to be contacted regarding the Synapex Ambassador Program.")
    
    Behavior: Conditio

{% enddoc %}
